        <abstract> 
<p>Sends calculations of angles of elevation [of sea-bottom, for <hi rend="italic">South America</hi>?].</p>  
<p>Swale has sent <hi rend="italic">Lady Willoughby’s diary</hi>, which EAD will forward to CD.</p> 
